1) PERIODS
    a) GET /period/list

2) CHARGES

    - POST /charge/list/period/${period}

        return summary for a given period

        $service_name,$service_type,$zone,$service_id,$created,$dropped
            $charge_type,$charge_area,$amount,$units

    - POST /charge/service/${service}/period/${period}

    

        return detailed info for a given period

    - GET /charge/service/${service}/period/${period}/unit

        return simulation for next unit charges


3) Pricing

    - GET /pricing/${service_name}/${service_type}/${zone}/${size}/${datetime}
